  <section class="problem-section">
    <div class="problem-container">
      <h2>🚨 The Water Crisis We're Solving</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Real evidence from Tamil Nadu's water bodies showing urgent environmental threats</p>
      <div class="problem-grid">
        <!-- Algae/Chlorophyll Problem -->
        <div class="problem-card">
          <img src="/images/algae-pollution.jpg" alt="Algae pollution in Coimbatore water body">
          <div class="problem-content">
            <span class="location-badge">📍 Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu</span>
            <h3>🦠 Excessive Algal Blooms</h3>
            <p>This image shows severe <strong>algal bloom pollution</strong> caused by excess nutrients and high chlorophyll-a concentrations in local water bodies.</p>
            <p><strong>Environmental Impact:</strong></p>
            <ul class="impact-list">
              <li>🐟 <strong>Fish kills:</strong> Depletes dissolved oxygen, suffocating aquatic life</li>
              <li>☠️ <strong>Toxic blooms:</strong> Some algae produce harmful toxins affecting wildlife and humans</li>
              <li>💧 <strong>Water contamination:</strong> Makes water unsafe for drinking, irrigation, and recreation</li>
              <li>🌡️ <strong>Ecosystem disruption:</strong> Blocks sunlight to underwater plants, destroying habitats</li>
              <li>⚠️ <strong>Health risks:</strong> Exposure can cause skin irritation, respiratory problems, and gastrointestinal illness</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Plastic Pollution Problem -->
        <div class="problem-card">
          <img src="/images/plastic-pollution.jpg" alt="Plastic debris along riverbank in Coimbatore">
          <div class="problem-content">
            <span class="location-badge">📍 Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu</span>
            <h3>🗑️ Plastic & Solid Waste Pollution</h3>
            <p>Visible plastic debris and solid waste accumulation along riverbanks and water bodies, creating long-term environmental damage.</p>
            <p><strong>Environmental Impact:</strong></p>
            <ul class="impact-list">
              <li>🐢 <strong>Wildlife harm:</strong> Animals ingest or become entangled in plastic waste</li>
              <li>🔬 <strong>Microplastics:</strong> Break down into tiny particles that enter the food chain</li>
              <li>💀 <strong>Toxic leaching:</strong> Chemicals from plastics contaminate water and soil</li>
              <li>🌊 <strong>Waterway blockage:</strong> Restricts water flow and increases flood risk</li>
              <li>🏞️ <strong>Habitat destruction:</strong> Smothers aquatic vegetation and spawning grounds</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 3rem; padding: 2rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); border-radius: 12px; color: white;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.8rem;">🎯 Our SIH 2025 Solution</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
          R-TECH's autonomous robotic multispectral radiometer system continuously monitors water quality parameters including 
          <strong>chlorophyll-a levels, turbidity, plastic signatures, and pH</strong>. Our data trains and validates 
          satellite observations from <strong>OceanSat-3 OCM and Sentinel-2/3</strong>, providing real-time alerts to authorities 
          for immediate action. This cost-effective solution aligns with India's Ganga Rejuvenation Mission and Jal Jeevan Mission.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


